Name: Cubyrinth
About the game: Cubyrinth is a 3D puzzle game. Will you be able to navigate and find the correct solution in the labyrinth located on the 6 sides of the cube? To complete the labyrinths, you can use highlight mode, which allows you to see already visited areas, as well as skip points, which allow you to skip too complex labyrinths (skip points will be given for every 3 completed labyrinths). Game Features: An infinite number of labyrinths. Each labyrinth is located on 6 sides of the cube. Each labyrinth is unique, because they all are auto-generated.
